If you just want a move that's fun to watch, Thor would fit the bill.  It's not going to be intellectually stimulating, but what super hero movie is?  Thor is eye candy, the fight scenes are fun, and the ending is sweet.  Overall an enjoyable way to spend an hour and a half.
Very enjoyable movie!
